703d90786f8cd87be5a78b","tid":1618621,"uid":78666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4603c812b4cbbdc08f554014600907038c479af5","tid":1618621,"uid":17678,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T07:56:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>鳩得嚟又幾有意思 竟然11集就完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>昨晚木綿花香港首播放左上一集條片<br />\n到依家都未放到11集出黎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://Anime1.me\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FAnime1.me&d=A2ufI7QLpLp1ny1o1CjT3pLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=d698e32f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Anime1.me</a> / 動漫花園 睇住先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T10:38:56.000Z","msg":"本身仲想盡力支持一下香港正版<br />\n無辦法啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今集最後一集<br />\n真係唔捨得<br />\n最初就咁聽個名，真係對呢套野完全提唔起興趣<br />\n睇其他新番介紹既片、又覺得好似唔錯，先真係追睇<br />\n<br />\n最後係絕對無後悔既<br />\n成套作品有好多唔同既元素<br />\n令人感動既位都有好多<br />\n要好笑有好笑、要熱血有熱血、要中二又中二到爆<br />\n<br />\n其實真係一套好唔錯既作品<br />\n睇得真係好爽<br />\n<br />\n每個毒撚可能都有自己「廚」既野<br />\n係主流社會入面，大多都唔會被理解同接受<br />\n但當同「志同道合」既人一齊既時候<br />\n就可以擦出好多火花<br />\n<br />\n享受自己喜歡既野、投入自己喜歡既野<br />\n好好咁活出同追求所喜愛既野<br />\n我諗係睇呢套作品畀到我最大既啟發<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bccdfece72c236a24b2bc06b370683e7deaf8e51","tid":1618621,"uid":78666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T10:42:43.000Z","msg":"最後送畀大家既回憶<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sFpGSXa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsFpGSXa.png&h=ff9497b6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"67b8db3e649f09f39bde4bf8f34bedef0982423e","tid":1618621,"uid":303244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T10:45:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"de612473b870e1adbb6c86302ba300fd0c087e40","tid":1618621,"uid":13151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bccdfece72c236a24b2bc06b370683e7deaf8e51","tid":1618621,"uid":78666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T10:42:43.000Z","msg":"最後送畀大家既回憶<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sFpGSXa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsFpGSXa.png&h=ff9497b6&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T16:39:28.000Z","msg":"女主gfable<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}